parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jacob Addington ROSE.
casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jacob Addington ROSE.
No. D-2736.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 4, 2013.
Jacob Addington Rose, of West Palm Beach, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
